{"tid":1551020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"IG 係咪又死咗？","createTime":"2019-09-07T20:21:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T16:18:24.000Z","uid":319216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"73d5871487dc4e48a50d4f0091000d70a46892fb","tid":1551020,"uid":319216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T20:21:54.000Z","msg":"如題"},{"pid":"0b1ffa5ece427601a4e862bb40aa64c3bec9fc4e","tid":1551020,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T20:22:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3692c36c8f7271fd7944d8ed5512b5bc49fb1763","tid":1551020,"uid":319216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T20:22:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"84569b81394f245959cedd1075942f2a2657adbb","tid":1551020,"uid":319216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T20:22:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"22ec3e70d3d414789b9a93f5b73ae0a1e7016f0c","tid":1551020,"uid":319216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T20:22:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2929024c5d9c0b38e3934940ed4c3fb359a88edc","tid":1551020,"uid":319216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"